Package: nightingale-deps
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Nightingale build deps
 Nightingale media player is a digital jukebox and Web browser mash-up.
 It supports extensions and feathers (skins). Like Firefox/Iceweasel,
 it is built from the Mozilla cross-platform and open source framework,
 and based on Songbird.
 .
 This package contains the files needed to build Nightingale.

